body_html:
I have built Tensoflow using bazel.
I have taken the libraries from tensorflow and used in android ndk, by stetting abi as either of 'arm64-v8a' or 'armeabiv-7a' and am executing
tensorflow::Status s = session->Create(tensorflow_graph); in android ndk from
https://github.com/miyosuda/TensorFlowAndroidMNIST/blob/master/jni-build/jni/tensorflow_jni.cc

More specifically from below attached file

tensorflow_jni.txt

I have built Tensoflow using bazel. 
I have taken the libraries from tensorflow and used in android ndk, by stetting abi as either of  'arm64-v8a' or 'armeabiv-7a' and am executing 
tensorflow::Status s = session->Create(tensorflow_graph); in android ndk from 
https://github.com/miyosuda/TensorFlowAndroidMNIST/blob/master/jni-build/jni/tensorflow_jni.cc

More specifically from below attached file

[tensorflow_jni.txt](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/1049525/tensorflow_jni.txt)
